On Saturday, February 05, 2005, at 05:21PM, Phil Cappellini <philcappellini(-at-)hotmail.com> wrote:

>Where can I get a correct nose panel for my 72 van?
>
>It appear as if all replacement nose panels are for the 73 to 79 models. The 
>signals are in the wrong place and the emblem is raised.

Wrong place is a 73 design. Raised emblem is VW Brazil bodywork style.

The panel you want is NLA. You have to perform this conversion to the available panel:

http://www.metwiz.com/nose/nose.html

